[00:00.000]作词 : Selena Gomez/Marshmello/Andrew Wotman/Louis Bell/Brian D. Lee/Alexandra Tamposi/Carl Rosen
[00:00.000][by:Novachy]
[00:01.000]作曲 : Selena Gomez/Marshmello/Andrew Wotman/Louis Bell/Brian D. Lee/Alexandra Tamposi/Carl Rosen
[00:09.130]In your eyes, there's a heavy blue
[00:09.130]在你的眼眸中，那充满了忧郁
[00:12.610]One to love, and one to lose
[00:12.610]左眼蕴藏爱意 右眼闪烁黯然
[00:16.340]Sweet divine, a heavy truth
[00:16.340]于甜蜜中却预感到事实的沉重
[00:20.030]Water or wine, don't make me choose
[00:20.030]水还是酒,别把我逼到两难的境地
[00:23.590]I wanna feel the way that we did that summer night, night
[00:23.590]我只想重温我们曾一起共度的仲夏之夜
[00:30.790]Drunk on a feeling, alone with the stars in the sky
[00:30.790]独自在醉意朦胧间仰望繁星点点
[00:38.000]I've been running through the jungle
[00:38.000]我在丛林中不断奔跑
[00:40.020]I've been running with the wolves
[00:40.020]我和狼群一同前行
[00:41.940]To get to you, to get to you
[00:41.940]只为追寻你 前往你身旁
[00:45.740]I've been down the darkest alleys
[00:45.740]我一路沿着墨色浓重的小径前行
[00:47.670]Saw the dark side of the moon
[00:47.670]甚至都看到了月球的背面
[00:49.390]To get to you, to get to you
[00:49.390]只为追寻你 前往你身旁
[00:53.310]I've looked for love in every stranger
[00:53.310]我在每个过客的心中搜索爱的踪迹
[00:55.450]Took too much to ease the anger
[00:55.450]喝下太多的酒才稍稍缓解心头之愤
[00:57.240]All for you, yeah, all for you
[00:57.240]都是为了你 都是因为你
[01:01.040]I've been running through the jungle
[01:01.040]我在丛林中不断奔跑
[01:02.980]I've been crying with the wolves
[01:02.980]我和狼群一起嗥鸣
[01:04.720]To get to you, to get to you, only get to you
[01:04.720]只为追寻你 前往你身旁 将你找寻
